tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
    visitor_id INT,
    page_visited VARCHAR(255),
    visit_duration_minutes INT,
    entry_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    exit_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url TEXT,
    visitor_id INT,
    visit_time TIMESTAMP,
    traffic_source TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE marketing_strategies (
    strategy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    strategy_name TEXT,
    target_audience TEXT,
    conversion_rate FLOAT,
    assigned_budget DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE user_demographics (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_name VARCHAR(100),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE marketing_campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(100),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE website_visitors (
    visitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visit_date DATE,
    website_page VARCHAR(255),
    visitor_country VARCHAR(50),
    visit_duration_minutes INT
)

CREATE TABLE page_views (
    page_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visit_date DATE,
    website_page VARCHAR(255),
    visit_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE marketing_campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(100),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE traffic_sources (
    source_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    source_name VARCHAR(100),
    source_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE ad_clicks (
    click_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ad_id INT,
    click_date DATE,
    click_count INT
)
